textBeforeTable: Missouri captured their first conference title in school history in 2012. Oklahoma State leads the conference with 11 overall conference titles with the last coming in 2011. The 2013 Big 12 Wrestling Championship will be held on Saturday, March 9, at the Gallagher-Iba Arena in Stillwater, Okla. It marks the third time Oklahoma State will host the event and the first since 2008.
